{"id":431,"ayahs":[{"number":23,"arabic":"وَلَا تَنفَعُ ٱلشَّفَٰعَةُ عِندَهُۥٓ إِلَّا لِمَنْ أَذِنَ لَهُۥ ۚ حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا فُزِّعَ عَن قُلُوبِهِمْ قَالُوا۟ مَاذَا قَالَ رَبُّكُمْ ۖ قَالُوا۟ ٱلْحَقَّ ۖ وَهُوَ ٱلْعَلِىُّ ٱلْكَبِيرُ","translation":"And, before Him, intercession can be of no avail [to any] save one in whose case He may have granted leave [there for]: so much so that when the terror [of the Last Hour] is lifted from their hearts, they [who have been resurrected] will ask [one an­other], “What has your Sustainer decreed [for you]?” - [to which] the others will answer, “Whatever is true and deserved - for He alone is exalted, great!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3629.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":26349,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26350,"position":2,"arabic":"تَنفَعُ","translation":"উপকার দিবে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26351,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلشَّفَـٰعَةُ","translation":"কোনো সুপারিশ","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26352,"position":4,"arabic":"عِندَهُۥٓ","translation":"কাছে তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26353,"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26354,"position":6,"arabic":"لِمَنْ","translation":"জন্যে যার","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26355,"position":7,"arabic":"أَذِنَ","translation":"তিনি অনুমতি দিবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26356,"position":8,"arabic":"لَهُۥ ۚ","translation":"জন্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26358,"position":9,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ","translation":"এমনকি","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26359,"position":10,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26360,"position":11,"arabic":"فُزِّعَ","translation":"দূর হয়ে যাবে (ভয়)","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26361,"position":12,"arabic":"عَن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26362,"position":13,"arabic":"قُلُوبِهِمْ","translation":"অন্তরগুলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26363,"position":14,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলবে( সুপারিশকারীদের)","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26364,"position":15,"arabic":"مَاذَا","translation":"\"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26365,"position":16,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"বলেছেন\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26366,"position":17,"arabic":"رَبُّكُمْ ۖ","translation":"রব তোমাদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26368,"position":18,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26369,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱلْحَقَّ ۖ","translation":"\"(যা)সত্য\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26371,"position":20,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26372,"position":21,"arabic":"ٱلْعَلِىُّ","translation":"সুউচ্চ","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26373,"position":22,"arabic":"ٱلْكَبِيرُ","translation":"সুমহান","audioUrl":"wbw/034_023_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26374,"position":23,"arabic":"٢٣","translation":"(২৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":24,"arabic":"۞ قُلْ مَن يَرْزُقُكُم مِّنَ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۖ قُلِ ٱللَّهُ ۖ وَإِنَّآ أَوْ إِيَّاكُمْ لَعَلَىٰ هُدًى أَوْ فِى ضَلَٰلٍۢ مُّبِينٍۢ","translation":"Say: “Who is it that provides for you sus­tenance out of the heavens and the earth?” Say: “It is God. And, behold, either we [who believe in Him] or you [who deny His oneness] are on the right path, or have clearly gone astray!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3630.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":27366,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27367,"position":2,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"\"কে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27368,"position":3,"arabic":"يَرْزُقُكُم","translation":"জীবিকা দেন আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27369,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27370,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27371,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۖ","translation":"ও পৃথিবী (হ'তে)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27373,"position":7,"arabic":"قُلِ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27374,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۖ","translation":"\"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27376,"position":9,"arabic":"وَإِنَّآ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27377,"position":10,"arabic":"أَوْ","translation":"অথবা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27378,"position":11,"arabic":"إِيَّاكُمْ","translation":"তোমরা (কোনো এক পক্ষ)","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27379,"position":12,"arabic":"لَعَلَىٰ","translation":"অবশ্যই উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27380,"position":13,"arabic":"هُدًى","translation":"সৎপথের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27381,"position":14,"arabic":"أَوْ","translation":"অথবা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27382,"position":15,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে (রয়েছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27383,"position":16,"arabic":"ضَلَـٰلٍۢ","translation":"বিভ্রান্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27384,"position":17,"arabic":"مُّبِينٍۢ","translation":"সুস্পষ্ট\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_024_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27385,"position":18,"arabic":"٢٤","translation":"(২৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":25,"arabic":"قُل لَّا تُسْـَٔلُونَ عَمَّآ أَجْرَمْنَا وَلَا نُسْـَٔلُ عَمَّا تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"Say: “Neither shall you be called to account for whatever we may have become guilty of, nor shall we be called to account for whatever you are doing.”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3631.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":28435,"position":1,"arabic":"قُل","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28436,"position":2,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"\"না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28437,"position":3,"arabic":"تُسْـَٔلُونَ","translation":"তোমাদের জিজ্ঞাসা করা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28438,"position":4,"arabic":"عَمَّآ","translation":"ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28439,"position":5,"arabic":"أَجْرَمْنَا","translation":"আমরা অপরাধ করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28440,"position":6,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28441,"position":7,"arabic":"نُسْـَٔلُ","translation":"আমাদের জিজ্ঞেস করা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28442,"position":8,"arabic":"عَمَّا","translation":"ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28443,"position":9,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা কাজ করছো\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_025_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28444,"position":10,"arabic":"٢٥","translation":"(২৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":26,"arabic":"قُلْ يَجْمَعُ بَيْنَنَا رَبُّنَا ثُمَّ يَفْتَحُ بَيْنَنَا بِٱلْحَقِّ وَهُوَ ٱلْفَتَّاحُ ٱلْعَلِيمُ","translation":"Say: “Our Sustainer will bring us all together [on Judgment Day], and then He will lay open the truth between us, in justice - for He alone is the One who opens all truth, the All-Knowing!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3632.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":29351,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29352,"position":2,"arabic":"يَجْمَعُ","translation":"\"একত্র করবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29353,"position":3,"arabic":"بَيْنَنَا","translation":"মাঝে আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29354,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبُّنَا","translation":"রব আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29355,"position":5,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29356,"position":6,"arabic":"يَفْتَحُ","translation":"তিনি মীমাংসা করে দিবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29357,"position":7,"arabic":"بَيْنَنَا","translation":"মাঝে আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29358,"position":8,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَقِّ","translation":"ভাবে সঠিক","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29359,"position":9,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29360,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْفَتَّاحُ","translation":"শ্রেষ্ঠ বিচারক","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29361,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْعَلِيمُ","translation":"সর্বজ্ঞ\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_026_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29362,"position":12,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"قُلْ أَرُونِىَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَلْحَقْتُم بِهِۦ شُرَكَآءَ ۖ كَلَّا ۚ بَلْ هُوَ ٱللَّهُ ٱلْعَزِيزُ ٱلْحَكِيمُ","translation":"Say: “Point out to me those [beings] that you have joined with Him [in your minds] as partners [in His divinity]! Nay - nay, but He [alone] is God, the Almighty, the Wise!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3633.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":30324,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30325,"position":2,"arabic":"أَرُونِىَ","translation":"\"তোমরা দেখাও তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30326,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদেরকে) যাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30327,"position":4,"arabic":"أَلْحَقْتُم","translation":"সংযুক্ত করেছো তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30328,"position":5,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"সাথে তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30329,"position":6,"arabic":"شُرَكَآءَ ۖ","translation":"শরিক হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30331,"position":7,"arabic":"كَلَّا ۚ","translation":"কখনও না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30333,"position":8,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30334,"position":9,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30335,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30336,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْعَزِيزُ","translation":"মহাপরাক্রমশালী","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30337,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْحَكِيمُ","translation":"প্রজ্ঞাময়\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_027_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30338,"position":13,"arabic":"٢٧","translation":"(২৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":28,"arabic":"وَمَآ أَرْسَلْنَٰكَ إِلَّا كَآفَّةًۭ لِّلنَّاسِ بَشِيرًۭا وَنَذِيرًۭا وَلَٰكِنَّ أَكْثَرَ ٱلنَّاسِ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"NOW [as for thee, O Muhammad,] We have not sent thee otherwise than to mankind at large, to be a herald of glad tidings and a warner; but most people do not understand [this],","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3634.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":31312,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَآ","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31313,"position":2,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَـٰكَ","translation":"আমরা পাঠিয়েছি তোমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31314,"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31315,"position":4,"arabic":"كَآفَّةًۭ","translation":"সমগ্র","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31316,"position":5,"arabic":"لِّلنَّاسِ","translation":"জন্যে মানবজাতির","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31317,"position":6,"arabic":"بَشِيرًۭا","translation":"সুসংবাদ দাতারূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31318,"position":7,"arabic":"وَنَذِيرًۭا","translation":"ও সতর্ককারী রূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31319,"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنَّ","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31320,"position":9,"arabic":"أَكْثَرَ","translation":"অধিকাংশ","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31321,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسِ","translation":"মানুষ","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31322,"position":11,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31323,"position":12,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"তারা জানে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_028_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31324,"position":13,"arabic":"٢٨","translation":"(২৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":29,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُونَ مَتَىٰ هَٰذَا ٱلْوَعْدُ إِن كُنتُمْ صَٰدِقِينَ","translation":"and so they ask, “When is this promise [of resurrection and judgment] to be fulfilled? [Answer this, O you who believe in it,] if you are men of truth!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3635.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":32299,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُونَ","translation":"এবং তারা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_029_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32300,"position":2,"arabic":"مَتَىٰ","translation":"\"কখন","audioUrl":"wbw/034_029_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32301,"position":3,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","translation":"সেই","audioUrl":"wbw/034_029_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32302,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْوَعْدُ","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি(পূর্ণ হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/034_029_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32303,"position":5,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/034_029_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32304,"position":6,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা হও","audioUrl":"wbw/034_029_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32305,"position":7,"arabic":"صَـٰدِقِينَ","translation":"সত্যবাদী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_029_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32306,"position":8,"arabic":"٢٩","translation":"(২৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":30,"arabic":"قُل لَّكُم مِّيعَادُ يَوْمٍۢ لَّا تَسْتَـْٔخِرُونَ عَنْهُ سَاعَةًۭ وَلَا تَسْتَقْدِمُونَ","translation":"Say: “There has been appointed for you a Day, which you can neither delay nor advance by a single moment.”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3636.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":33132,"position":1,"arabic":"قُل","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33133,"position":2,"arabic":"لَّكُم","translation":"\"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33134,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّيعَادُ","translation":"নির্দিষ্ট সময়","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33135,"position":4,"arabic":"يَوْمٍۢ","translation":"দিনে (যা)","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33136,"position":5,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33137,"position":6,"arabic":"تَسْتَـْٔخِرُونَ","translation":"তোমরা পিছিয়ে দিতে পারবে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33138,"position":7,"arabic":"عَنْهُ","translation":"থেকে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33139,"position":8,"arabic":"سَاعَةًۭ","translation":"মুহূর্তকাল","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33140,"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33141,"position":10,"arabic":"تَسْتَقْدِمُونَ","translation":"তোমরা এগিয়ে আনতে পারবে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_030_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":33142,"position":11,"arabic":"٣٠","translation":"(৩০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":31,"arabic":"وَقَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ لَن نُّؤْمِنَ بِهَٰذَا ٱلْقُرْءَانِ وَلَا بِٱلَّذِى بَيْنَ يَدَيْهِ ۗ وَلَوْ تَرَىٰٓ إِذِ ٱلظَّٰلِمُونَ مَوْقُوفُونَ عِندَ رَبِّهِمْ يَرْجِعُ بَعْضُهُمْ إِلَىٰ بَعْضٍ ٱلْقَوْلَ يَقُولُ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱسْتُضْعِفُوا۟ لِلَّذِينَ ٱسْتَكْبَرُوا۟ لَوْلَآ أَنتُمْ لَكُنَّا مُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"And [yet,] those who are bent on denying the truth do say, “We shall never believe in this Qur’an, and neither in whatever there still remains of earlier revelations!” But if thou couldst only see [how it will be on Judgment Day,] when these evildoers shall be made to stand before their Sustainer, hurling reproaches back and forth at one another! Those [of them] who had been weak [on earth] will say unto those who had gloried in their arrogance: “Had it not been for you, we would certainly have been believers!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3637.mp3","surahId":34,"words":[{"id":34107,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"এবং বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34108,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34109,"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34110,"position":4,"arabic":"لَن","translation":"\"কখনও না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34111,"position":5,"arabic":"نُّؤْمِنَ","translation":"বিশ্বাস করবো আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34112,"position":6,"arabic":"بِهَـٰذَا","translation":"উপর এই","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34113,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانِ","translation":"কুরআনের","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34114,"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34115,"position":9,"arabic":"بِٱلَّذِى","translation":"উপর যা","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34116,"position":10,"arabic":"بَيْنَ","translation":"মাঝে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34117,"position":11,"arabic":"يَدَيْهِ ۗ","translation":"হাতের তার\"","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34119,"position":12,"arabic":"وَلَوْ","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34120,"position":13,"arabic":"تَرَىٰٓ","translation":"তুমি দেখতে","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34121,"position":14,"arabic":"إِذِ","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/034_031_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34122,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمُونَ","translation":"সীমালঙ্ঘনকারীদের